test-drive
------------------------------------------
Simple testing framework

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.4-2
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libgfortran5-11.3.0-1
  libquadmath0-11.3.0-1
  libtest-drive-devel-0.4.0-1bl1
  libtest-drive0-0.4.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.8.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.38-1
  cmake-3.20.0-1
  cygport-0.35.0-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-fortran-11.3.0-1
  meson-0.61.4-1
  ninja-1.10.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/fortran-lang/test-drive

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/fortran-lang/test-drive/archive/refs/tags/v0.4.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack test-drive-0.4.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./test-drive-0.4.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/test-drive-0.4.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/test-drive-0.4.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtest-drive0-0.4.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtest-drive-devel-0.4.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(test-drive)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/test-drive.README
  /usr/share/doc/test-drive/LICENSE-Apache
  /usr/share/doc/test-drive/LICENSE-MIT
  /usr/share/doc/test-drive/README.md

(libtest-drive0)
  /usr/bin/cygtest-drive-0.dll

(libtest-drive-devel)
  /usr/include/testdrive.mod
  /usr/include/testdrive_version.mod
  /usr/lib/libtest-drive.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/test-drive.pc

